column5: This could be ancient news for all I know, but was there not at one point a 'hook-ups' forum on here?  I was looking for it earlier today, and realized I hadn't noticed it in quite some time.  So I guess what I'm saying is, I had a guy cancel on me for a trip tomorrow to the Hwy. 118 corridor to do some troutin', who wants to come?
By stupid question I thought you meant something like ....  What would chairs look like if our knees bent the other way?   Randy
hook Up" section was deleted once everyone found a partner?  edit to add....jokes are better when they are spelled proper....
lmao...cant be pretty and smart....but i can be content with neither...
wish i could tag along, I have still yet to ice any fish in my life and after buying my first ice combo the other day im really starting to fiend!!!
Is it wrong that I found that both funny and intriguing? I actually tried to picture it.  haha
Did you find someone to fish with... ? And this worked just fine!
